{"tid":1808292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【勞工界】民主派新工會湧現 勢搶攻特首選委會","createTime":"2020-01-02T09:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:31:42.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5793db3f57fe9e319daa79faa0de3391d9ea5141","tid":1808292,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"民主派想搶攻2020年立法會選舉及特首選委會中一些長期被建制派壟斷的議席，當中包括飲食界、勞工界等，近月各行各業的民主派支持者相繼在其工作界別組織工會，職工盟主席吳敏兒今日出席電台節目中指，近月收到不少成立工會的查詢，但她坦言，即使有新工會成立，亦已來不及爭奪下屆立法會功能界別的勞工界議席，因除了數量上要有約400多個新工會，有關工會亦要在選舉前一年已完成登記。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民主派或要待2024年的立法會才能搶攻勞工界議席，但吳敏兒指，可把期望放在明年的特首選委會選舉，新工會還可參與每兩年一次的勞顧會選舉：「如果新成立嘅工會夠多，就可以喺有勞工議席嘅選舉平台上競爭，唔會畀佢哋（建制派）自動當選，呢個絕對唔會係難事。」<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒指，全香港工會約有600至700個，約300個是公務員工會，另外300多個是建制工會，只有不多於100個是獨立的工會，所以民主派以往也在全票制下難以攻陷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200102/60442303?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60442303%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b19d7fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60442303%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=69da70e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200102/60442303?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"94fe99e130b313438d0211db3408e6e585ba4686","tid":1808292,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"［愈辨愈明］點解港獨被佛地魔化？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"708fd245d04cf7dd2cc5cd808f16932aaf178707","tid":1808292,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}